# Project-wide .dockerignore for the root docker-compose build context.

**/.DS_Store
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*.log

# Test /
**/TestResults/
**/coverage/

# Local env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# dotnet
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/

# node
**/node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-*.log*
**/.npm/
**/.next/
**/dist/

# Local Postgres sandbox
**/pgdata/
**/pgsocket/
**/pglog

# Git
**/.git/

# Docker / compose meta
**/.dockerignore
**/Dockerfile*
**/docker-compose*.yml
